imageDescription: In the image, a woman stands tall amidst a colorful cityscape, her hair billowing with smoke. She holds a necklace made of miniature figures, each representing a boy she has conquered. The vibrant city represents her power and allure, while the smoke symbolizes her intoxicating presence. It captures the boldness and confidence of the song's lyrics, showcasing her unapologetic attitude towards her actions.
